articles.title: E-bike brand VanMoof declared bankrupt | Cyclingnews - Cyclingnews
articles.description: Existing orders may not be fulfilled, spare parts are currently unavailable, but functionality for existing bikes is confirmed for now
articles.content:
VanMoof, the Dutch electric bike brand, has been forced to declare bankruptcy after the brand's co-founding brothers, Ties and Taco Carlier, failed to find investment to save it.
